snippet: Phillip Lee of the Kimchi Taco truck opens Kimchi Grill in Prospect Heights; Mile End Sandwich, a spinoff of the Brooklyn restaurant, comes to Manhattan.
abstract: Restaurants Kimchi Grill, Mile End Sandwich, Pranzo, Pink Tea Cup Chicken and Waffles and Tavern 29, open in New York.
lead_paragraph: Phillip Lee of the Kimchi Taco truck opens Kimchi Grill in Prospect Heights; Mile End Sandwich, a spinoff of the Brooklyn restaurant, comes to Manhattan.

headline.seo: Kimchi Grill and Mile End Sandwich Open
